pull.title: net: Add missing verification of IPv6 address in CNetAddr::GetIn6Addr(...)
pull.body: Add missing verification of IPv6 address in `CNetAddr::GetIn6Addr(...)`.

events.message: net: Add missing verification of IPv6 address in CNetAddr::GetIn6Addr(...)

events.body:
utACK 2fb0066b9932f3725a5a0533530453c6da4010ce

Only ever called from within netaddress.cpp (inside `if (IsIPv6())` block), so this condition is guaranteed to never be true, but it is a bool already, and it is public.
